            <div class="alert alert-success" id="recent-changes">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">📝 Recent Changes (v1.00 - Jan 9, 2026)</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 5px 0 0 20px;">
                    <li><strong>Initial Documentation:</strong> Created comprehensive documentation for AiMessage model</li>
                    <li><strong>Agent Types:</strong> Documented 5 supported agent types (documentation, helpdesk, ency, beekeeping, hamradio)</li>
